The multi-million Gemz residential project in Al Furjan, an upscale neighbourhood, gated community, and property development in the Jebel Ali district, Dubai, United Arab Emirates, has officially been launched by Danube Properties, one of the top 5th properties developer in UAE. The project is reportedly in line with Danube Properties‘ aim to offer an enhanced lifestyle accompanied by top-quality amenities for citizens and their families. The Gemz residential project in Al Furjan will feature one-bedroom, two-bedroom, and three-bedroom apartments in the buzzing city of Dubai. The units range from 410 square feet to 2,253 square feet and currently have a starting price of AED 550,000. The exclusive, luxury development surrounded by CCTV cameras will include a children’s play area, a BBQ area alongside lush green parks, and a parking area. Read Also Construction of Creek Views I at Dubai Healthcare City in Dubai, UAE, Almost Complete There will also be retail outlets, restaurants, schools, a mosque, and a shopping mall. In an effort towards encouraging a healthier and more active lifestyle, the project will also feature a gym, a swimming pool, and sporting facilities. The Gemz residential project is a part of a master-planned community that aims to provide residents with a lifestyle that is elite in every way. The project is within four minutes proximity to the Sheikh Zayed Road, and two minutes away from the proposed metro line. Additionally, the project will also be at a distance of merely 10 minutes away from the Al Maktoum International Airport. This is all in a strategic effort to ensure that residents live a peaceful lifestyle with convenient access to the finest entertainment, eating, and shopping options.